## This repo + Payload

- **Preferred CMS access:** `getPayload` in **Server Components**, **Route Handlers**, and **Server Actions** — **`payload-basics.mdc`**, **`payload-performance.mdc`** (`depth`, `select`).
- **Cache keys:** when wrapping Payload reads in **`unstable_cache`**, include anything that affects shape (e.g. **`depth`**) — see `utilities/getDocument.ts`.
- **REST from browser:** treat responses as **`unknown`** at boundaries (same discipline as **`payload-apis.mdc`**).

## Checklist

- [ ] No accidental client-side exposure of secrets or full Payload queries.
- [ ] Server Actions validated on the server; auth aligned with your app’s session/API rules.
- [ ] Streaming / parallel fetching patterns from [Fetching data](https://nextjs.org/docs/app/getting-started/fetching-data) when lists are heavy.

